title: HotArchiveBucketEntryType
description:
HotArchiveBucketEntryType is an XDR Enum defines as:

```text enum HotArchiveBucketEntryType { HOT_ARCHIVE_METAENTRY = -1, // Bucket metadata, should come first. HOT_ARCHIVE_ARCHIVED = 0,   // Entry is Archived HOT_ARCHIVE_LIVE = 1        // Entry was previously HOT_ARCHIVE_ARCHIVED, but // has been added back to the live BucketList. // Does not need to be persisted. }; ```
